  <h2>Gas furnaces: rare, but we service them</h2>
  <p>If your home has a gas or propane furnace, typically in newer New Tampa, Wesley Chapel, or Land O' Lakes communities, we handle the full scope safely:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Tune-ups, ignitor replacement, and flame-sensor cleaning.</li>
    <li>Gas valve service and blower motor repair.</li>
    <li>Heat exchanger inspection with a carbon monoxide check on every furnace visit.</li>
  </ul>

  <InContentCTA
